author: @leandrolopes718
content: I can't imagine how sad and sick someone must be to attack another person like this. Madonna is a brilliant individual who has built a brilliant career and has a strong will to live. You can count on one hand the artists who have reached her age and continue with the same energy, the same enthusiasm, without losing self-esteem, without losing their appreciation for the things they love. One day, you too will grow old and will wish to maintain youthfulness in your skin.
